1
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:41,160
Aling returns to the capital today.

2
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:43,759
I'll go to the Xiao Manor first to surprise her.

3
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,240
Your Majesty.

4
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,560
I found the true cause

5
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:50,120
of Madam Xiao and Young Master Xiao's deaths.

6
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,450
You caught the bandits?

7
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:53,759
Great.

8
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,640
Let Aling deal with them.

9
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,210
That way,

10
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,930
she won't blame herself for the past anymore.

11
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,040
Your Majesty.

12
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,940
It wasn't bandits.

13
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:04,380
It was the Xuanniao Division.

14
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,449
The Xuanniao Division?

15
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:10,880
Yes.

16
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,000
Royal Father's Xuanniao Division.

17
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,900
I don't think he's coming.

18
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,020
I stated my return date in the letter.

19
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,160
Yunxi will surely come to see me.

20
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,680
He is the Emperor now.

21
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,720
He must have a lot to deal with.

22
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:44,640
True.

23
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,960
He is the Emperor now.

24
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,000
It's not like before,

25
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:52,250
when he could sneak out of the palace whenever he wanted.

26
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,780
Before you marry into the palace,

27
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,160
it's not too late to change your mind.

28
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,680
Since he can't come here,

29
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,960
I'll go to the palace to find him.

30
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,530
A wife follows her husband.

31
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,600
General Xiao.

32
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,200
The Xiao family has been loyal for generations.

33
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,880
His Majesty doesn't want to implicate the Xiao Army,

34
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,720
or tarnish the Empress's reputation,

35
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:44,079
so he ordered me to arrest you secretly.

36
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,890
If you want to arrest me,

37
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,800
you must explain clearly

38
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,690
what crime I've committed.

39
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:54,880
General Xiao.

40
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,640
You conspired with the descendants

41
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,680
of ministers killed by the Xuanniao Tribe

42
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,280
to assassinate His Majesty.

43
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,220
Everyone else has been executed.

44
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,080
Why feign ignorance?

45
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:04,880
Nonsense!

46
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,520
I want to kill the Emperor?

47
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,040
How come I didn't know that?

48
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:08,640
General,

49
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:11,160
please return to the palace with me.

50
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,600
Let's see

51
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,080
if you have what it takes.

52
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,080
Stop!

53
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,420
Your Highness.

54
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,060
Who told you to tip him off?

55
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,720
Who told you to come here disguised as Xiao Rushan?

56
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,490
I want to save my father.

57
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:09,920
Ling'er.

58
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:12,140
You knocked me out and tied me up here.

59
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,680
What are you trying to do?

60
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,680
If one of us has to die,

61
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,140
I'd rather it be me.

62
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,880
How would you know

63
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,000
someone has to die?

64
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:29,920
Ling.

65
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,280
Xiao Ling!

66
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,560
Move!

67
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,960
I can't let you kill him.

68
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,560
Actually, the ones who killed your mother and brother

69
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,560
weren't bandits.

70
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:42,810
It was the late Emperor's Xuanniao Division.

71
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,640
The late Emperor?

72
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,600
Xuanniao Division?

73
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,680
Li Yunxi!

74
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,840
Yunxi.

75
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,520
It was your father

76
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,440
who killed my mother and brother.

77
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,100
About your family,

78
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,240
I can't tell you anything.

79
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,040
Yunxi,

80
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:14,900
this is the truth you've been hiding from me.

81
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,600
I got Mother and Brother killed.

82
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,100
I don't have a mother anymore.

83
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,650
It's not your fault.

84
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,680
So you knew everything.

85
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,650
I don't understand.

86
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:33,100
We clearly just didn't get along.

87
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,159
Why did it come to this?

88
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:35,800
Ling.

89
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,940
What makes you think I'd tell you?

90
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,159
Regarding General Xiao,

91
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,490
I will explain it to you myself.

92
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,440
No matter how you explain,

93
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:50,040
I will never forgive you.

94
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,960
Then kill me.

95
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,520
And you'll never know the answer.

96
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,400
You'd rather have me hate you

97
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,640
than tell the truth.

98
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,440
Once I investigate the assassins outside the palace

99
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:05,000
who disguised themselves as the Xuanniao Tribe,

100
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,460
I will give you the answer.

101
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,680
You were afraid I'd get hurt,

102
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,420
so you shouldered everything for me.

103
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,040
You want me to stay?

104
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,000
Over my dead body.

105
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
Yet I've been hurting you all along.

106
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,280
Your heart

107
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,540
must be in so much pain.

108
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,680
A son pays for his father's sins.

109
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,920
I will kill you today

110
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,680
to avenge my wife and son.

111
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,760
Yunxi.

112
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,640
You've done so much for me.

113
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:44,440
This time,

114
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,010
it's my turn to protect you.

115
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:48,800
Ling.

116
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,340
What are you doing?

117
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,400
Ling'er.

118
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,200
He's the son of our enemy.

119
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,320
Why are you protecting him?

120
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,080
Father.

121
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,220
The Xiao family's feud

122
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,530
was caused by the late Emperor.

123
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,760
It has nothing to do with him.

124
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,320
You may leave now.

125
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,020
Let me apply the medicine for you.

126
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,160
It must be painful.

127
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,250
Why were you so foolish?

128
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,640
Do you know,

129
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,600
this breaks my heart?

130
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,880
I would rather die under General Xiao's sword

131
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,760
than let you suffer like this.

132
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,320
When did you find out about that?

133
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,120
Two years ago.

134
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:32,250
So you didn't pick me up that day

135
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,440
because of this.

136
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,520
The day I returned to the capital,

137
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,850
I waited for you all day.

138
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:43,720
When I went to the palace to find you the next day,

139
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,920
I saw you hugging Liu Mianmian.

140
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,520
That day, outside the teahouse,

141
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,500
she overheard the conversation.

142
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,410
She used it to blackmail me.

143
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:02,250
My heart belongs to you, Your Majesty.

144
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,960
Please let me be your woman.

145
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,800
Stop dreaming.

146
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,600
In this life,

147
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,800
I will only marry Aling.

148
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:16,180
But the Late Emperor killed her mother and brother.

149
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,120
There is a blood feud between you.

150
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,600
You can never be together.

151
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,980
How do you know about this?

152
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,200
If you refuse to marry me,

153
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:30,400
I'll tell Xiaoling the truth.

154
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,420
Don't you dare!

155
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,720
Your Majesty.

156
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,880
If you agree to my terms,

157
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:44,200
I'll take this secret to my grave.

158
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,240
Who is she?

159
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:06,370
Since I've given you the Phoenix Seal,

160
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,840
I will keep my promise

161
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:10,250
and make you my Empress.

162
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,490
As for Mianmian,

163
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:13,780
she will enter the palace with you

164
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:16,240
as my Consort.

165
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,360
So,

166
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,520
this is what

167
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,970
you were blackmailed with.

168
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:25,810
I always thought

169
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,930
I could hide it from you.

170
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,720
I wanted to hide it for as long as I could.

171
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:35,610
That way,

172
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,530
I could keep you by my side for one more day.

173
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,560
I never thought

174
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:51,170
after everything we went through to be together,

175
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,000
it would end like this.

176
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,200
Get some rest.

177
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,120
I'm leaving.

178
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,160
Don't kill my father.

179
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,680
For what he has done,

180
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,400
I will give you an explanation.
